    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "These panpipes are made of what seems to be beat-up tin bound by frayed leather and look like they shouldn't function at all, but in skilled hands they emit a beautiful sound that beguiles the senses. While playing the pipes, you gain a +1 item bonus to Diplomacy and Performance checks.",
